714722f.title: Manhattan: 86th Street - Madison Avenue
714722f.text:
86th Street, south side, west from Madison (left, not shown) to Fifth (right) Aves., showing the newly constructed 22-story apartment house, the Adams. To the east of same is a portion of the Croydon and to the west, the Wm. Starr Miller residence. Aoross the roof of the latter appears a southwesterly view across the southern end of Central
Park.
About 1929.
James Smith.
